    "description": "在《Tiny Witch》中，你是一位负责管理位于满是地下城主的小镇的魔法商店的小女巫。启动你的咒语，解锁新的配方，并及时准备好最好的仆从，以免惹恼你的顾客。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 特点 </h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740310/extras/55fc02e1a47cc8fc24cca0e1b79d4d38.poster.avif?t=1758551549\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740310/extras/55fc02e1a47cc8fc24cca0e1b79d4d38.webm?t=1758551549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740310/extras/55fc02e1a47cc8fc24cca0e1b79d4d38.mp4?t=1758551549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>混合和制造仆从：</strong> 通过在研钵中混合或在大锅中煮沸来创建资源，然后在你的炼金桌上混合魔法资源来制造仆从！ <br><br></li><li> <strong>顾客和后果：</strong> 向顾客提供所需的仆从，否则就要承受后果！不同类型的顾客有不同的脾气和愿意给你小费的意愿。服务他们是你这个谦卑的小女巫店持久经营的关键。<br><br></li><li> <strong>扩展和体验：</strong> 购买新的资源、研钵等来改善你的商店！有不同的阶段，例如包装阶段，你可以购买装饰品、宠物，并添加新的工作台。管理你的小女巫的仆从制造商店，白天和晚上在森林、洞穴和沙漠中运营——这个大世界就是你的小女巫的牡蛎。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740310/extras/068018b64de426fb8b504ea7556e0d89.poster.avif?t=1758551549\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740310/extras/068018b64de426fb8b504ea7556e0d89.webm?t=1758551549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740310/extras/068018b64de426fb8b504ea7556e0d89.mp4?t=1758551549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
